an app made for the Lord, His people, and His Word

purpose: to help track spiritual life (as if you're taking care of a plant)

start - user is prompt to give their "spirit" a color (ball of smoke constantly turning/smoking)

survey:
- times for devo
- times for prayer
- season of life
- times and days for church, lifegroup, gatherings
- color of your "spirit"

IMPORTANT FEATURES:
- prayer requests
- answered prayers
- miracle of the day
- gratitude
- daily and weekly challenges (tell someone about Jesus today!)

features:
- CAN BE A WIDGET
- if no lifegroup/mentor yet, it recommends to nearest YROCK location
- calendar for quick view of all events, gatherings, LGs, LCCs, and SWC
- (Home) news for YROCK
- synced to bible app (if possible)
- SOS (bible, mentor/church leaders)
- add for event reminders
- encouragement to CONTINUE THE MISSION AND TO NOT GET SIDETRACKED!
- verses that bases off of their current devos/seasons
- quick notes for devo time or quiet time with the Lord
- MISSION WRAPPED [YEAR]

AI features:
- helps in assessing why you might be distant, feeling spiritually down, or empty
- encouragement if streak going well
- suggestions for the week if an alert was sent

TRACKING:
- streaks
- verses of encouragement, motivation, support, empowerment
- if it goes over a "spiritual threshold", it sends an alert/alarm that user's "spirit" is hungry/thirsty

1. tracks devotional time
2. tracks prayer time
3. tracks how many times attendance (church, lifegroup, gatherings, events)
4. tracks challenges


TO DO IN FUTURE:
